  <biospec_descr>
    <textblock>
      Collect 27 mL of blood to send (1) for extraction of DNA to the NIDDK Central Repository and
      (2) for measurement of glucose, C-peptide, and autoantibody analysis to a central blood
      laboratory.
    </textblock>
